  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\"Roll On Dice\"!</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096960/extras/cfcc0aefbd5f7329df61b13e90df683b.poster.avif?t=1753809980\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096960/extras/cfcc0aefbd5f7329df61b13e90df683b.webm?t=1753809980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096960/extras/cfcc0aefbd5f7329df61b13e90df683b.mp4?t=1753809980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Roll On Dice is a pretty simple puzzle game, where you just have to roll on other dice with a 6 sided dice. But it can become quite tricky if you don’t know well your faces. Indeed, in order to beat a dice, you will need to have your top face superior or equal to the one that you are rolling on, otherwise you will break your own…<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The game has over 50 puzzle levels to beat with this main rolling mechanic<br></li><li>The rhythm is pretty relaxing, take your time to solve each level<br></li><li>Enjoy the colorful graphics</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\"Roll On Dice\"!</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096960/extras/cfcc0aefbd5f7329df61b13e90df683b.poster.avif?t=1753809980\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096960/extras/cfcc0aefbd5f7329df61b13e90df683b.webm?t=1753809980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2096960/extras/cfcc0aefbd5f7329df61b13e90df683b.mp4?t=1753809980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Roll On Dice is a pretty simple puzzle game, where you just have to roll on other dice with a 6 sided dice. But it can become quite tricky if you don’t know well your faces. Indeed, in order to beat a dice, you will need to have your top face superior or equal to the one that you are rolling on, otherwise you will break your own…<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The game has over 50 puzzle levels to beat with this main rolling mechanic<br></li><li>The rhythm is pretty relaxing, take your time to solve each level<br></li><li>Enjoy the colorful graphics</li></ul>",
